 on the topic.) This, along with his <i>sui generis </i>phenotype, made him=
 a reliable punching bag for <b>Tucker Carlson </b>and <b>Greg Gutfeld </b>=
types, a poster child for CNN=E2=80=99s perceived liberal bias in the Trump=
